	<article id="post-3718" class="post-3718 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-accountability category-big-brother category-civil-liberties category-courage category-democracy category-intelligence category-machon category-manning category-media category-national-security category-privacy-2 category-snowden category-spies category-surveillance category-talks-2 category-war-2 category-whistleblowers category-wikileaks tag-accountability-2 tag-alexa-obrian tag-berlin tag-bill-binney tag-courage tag-diani-barreto tag-edward-snowden tag-intelligence-2 tag-media-2 tag-nsa tag-panopticon tag-spies-2 tag-surveillance-2 tag-tech tag-transmediale tag-whistleblowers-2 tag-wikileaks">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/03/circumventing-panopticon-transmediale-berlin.html" title="Permalink to Circumventing the Panopticon, Transmediale Berlin" rel="bookmark">Circumventing the Panopticon, Transmediale Berlin</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/03/circumventing-panopticon-transmediale-berlin.html" title="21:01" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2014-03-22T21:01:41+00:00" pubdate>March 22, 2014</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/03/circumventing-panopticon-transmediale-berlin.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>Last month I was on a panel dis­cus­sion at the Ber­lin Trans­me­diale con­fer­ence with <span class="caps">NSA</span> whis­tleblower Bill Bin­ney, Chelsea Man­ning rap­por­teur Alexa O’Brian, and act­iv­ist Diani Bar­reto. Here is the link to the <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6qxU1voSEDA">full two hour event</a>, and here is my speech:</p>
<p><img src="http://anniemachon.ch/wp-content/uploads/transmediale.png" alt="transmediale" width="706" height="397" class="placeholder alignleft size-full wp-image-3810" data-source="vimeo" data-id="89779675" /></p>
<p><a href="http://vimeo.com/89779675">Trans­me­diale, Ber­lin 2014</a> from <a href="http://vimeo.com/anniemachon">Annie Machon</a> on <a href="https://vimeo.com">Vimeo</a>.</p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
		<footer class="entry-meta">
