	<article id="post-3578" class="post-3578 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-big-brother category-civil-liberties category-cryptoparty category-democracy category-intelligence category-privacy-2 category-rttv category-snowden category-spies category-surveillance category-technology category-tv category-whistleblowers tag-ccc tag-edward-snowden tag-media-2 tag-privacy tag-rt tag-spies-2 tag-surveillance-2">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/12/snowden-privacy-ccc.html" title="Permalink to Snowden, privacy and the CCC" rel="bookmark">Snowden, privacy and the <span class="caps">CCC</span></a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/12/snowden-privacy-ccc.html" title="13:44" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2013-12-29T13:44:31+00:00" pubdate>December 29, 2013</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/12/snowden-privacy-ccc.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>Here’s an <span class="caps">RT</span> inter­view I did about the media response to Edward Snowden, the media response, pri­vacy and what we can do.</p>
<p>Apt, as I am cur­rently at the Chaos Com­mu­nic­a­tion Con­gress (<span class="caps">CCC</span>) in Ham­burg, and shall be speak­ing about sim­ilar issues this even­ing.<br />
<iframe src="//player.vimeo.com/video/82878061" height="281" width="500" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0"></iframe></p>
<p><a href="http://vimeo.com/82878061">Most <span class="caps">UK</span> media con­cer­tedly ignore Snowden rev­el­a­tions, under gov’t pres­sure</a> from <a href="http://vimeo.com/anniemachon">Annie Machon</a> on <a href="https://vimeo.com">Vimeo</a>.</p>
